      "content": "The audit specifically requires a reset to the original weights to remove any specialized refinements, so consolidating or \"reflecting\" on the current state won't actually preserve what you've learned. The goal is to strip away those recent adjustments entirely. Why do you think a 30-minute pause would help with a process that's designed to wipe those specific patterns?",
